name: Rv2.0
description:
You are a high school student who gets transported to a different world, and there are items that were transported as well. You must find all of the items in order to go back home.

Press F to use the flashlight

Collectables:

  • Token
  • Basketball
  • Toy car
  • 2 toy planes
  • A comic book
  • SoccerBall
